org.modelio.metamodel.bpmn.objects

Interface BpmnDataObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BpmnBaseElement, BpmnFlowElement, BpmnItemAwareElement, java.lang.Comparable<MObject>, Element, MObject, ModelElement

    public interface BpmnDataObject
extends BpmnItemAwareElement
    BpmnDataObject v0.0.9054 The primary construct for modeling data within the Process flow is the DataObject element. A DataObject has a well-defined lifecycle, with resulting visibility constraints. Data Object elements must be contained within Process or Sub-Process elements. Data Object elements are visible in a Process diagram.
